text: José António Gregório (born 12 August 1939) is a Portuguese wrestler. He competed in the men's Greco-Roman featherweight at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1939 births Category:Living people Category:Portuguese male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Portugal Category:Wrestlers at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Lisbon
